{"title":"enc","slug":"enc","date":"2021-02-14T06:50:41.067Z","updated":"2021-02-14T07:08:27.556Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/enc.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2021021414491033.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center"],"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=4838&page=2\">enc</a></p>\n<p>题目描述给出采用了某种编码方式</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Fady不是很理解加密与编码的区别 所以他使用编码而不是加密，给他的朋友传了一些秘密的消息。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>下载附件后得到的是一个txt文件，将其中ONE和ZERO 转化成0和1，然后转成字符串，可以发现为base64加密得到字符串，解密后得到是一串莫斯电码串，将莫斯电码翻译得到<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2021021414491033.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>有得到的字符串，经过玄学的添加字符可以得到最后的flag，<br>脚本如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">##with open(&#x27;enc&#x27;,&#x27;r&#x27;) as fp:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">##    m=fp.read()</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">##for i in m:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">##    if i == &#x27;Z&#x27;:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">##        print(1,end=&#x27;&#x27;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">##    if i==&#x27;N&#x27;:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">##        print(0,end=&#x27;&#x27;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> re</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> base64</span><br><span class=\"line\">m=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">t=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> m:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> i==<span class=\"string\">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        t+=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;0&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        t+=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;1&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">texta=re.findall(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;.&#123;8&#125;&#x27;</span>,t)</span><br><span class=\"line\">s=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> texta:</span><br><span class=\"line\">   s+=<span class=\"built_in\">chr</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(i,<span class=\"number\">2</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\">t=base64.b64decode(s)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(t)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}